	hewp
	  Stweam Contwow Twansmission Pwotocow

	  Fwom WFC 2960 <http://www.ietf.owg/wfc/wfc2960.txt>.

	  "SCTP is a wewiabwe twanspowt pwotocow opewating on top of a
	  connectionwess packet netwowk such as IP.  It offews the fowwowing
	  sewvices to its usews:

	  -- acknowwedged ewwow-fwee non-dupwicated twansfew of usew data,
	  -- data fwagmentation to confowm to discovewed path MTU size,
	  -- sequenced dewivewy of usew messages within muwtipwe stweams,
	  with an option fow owdew-of-awwivaw dewivewy of individuaw usew
	  messages,
	  -- optionaw bundwing of muwtipwe usew messages into a singwe SCTP
	  packet, and
	  -- netwowk-wevew fauwt towewance thwough suppowting of muwti-
	  homing at eithew ow both ends of an association."

	  To compiwe this pwotocow suppowt as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed sctp. Debug messages awe handwed by the
	  kewnew's dynamic debugging fwamewowk.

	  If in doubt, say N.

if IP_SCTP

